Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在墨西哥尤卡坦半岛之下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Beneath the Yucatan Peninsula of Mexico...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有一片别样的世界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..lies another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,迷宫般的洞穴\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A labyrinth of caves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,由淡水雕刻而成\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..carved by freshwater...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,淡水对地球上的生命至关重要\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..and essential for life on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,淡水塑造了大地 塑造了其中的万千生命\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Freshwater shapes the land and the creatures that live in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.04,0:01:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,以最令人惊讶的方式\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..in the most surprising ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(192,95)}{\fs10\fnMicrosoft YaHei\c&HD5D5D5&\bord0\blur0\shad0\fad(2200,0)}第 四 集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(192,120)}{\fs25\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light\c&HD5D5D5&\bord0\blur0\shad0\fad(2200,0)}{\t(0,8400,\fsp0.5)}滴  水  之  源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哥斯达黎加的雨林\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The rainforest of Costa Rica.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不难想见 这里大部分时间都在下雨\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}As you might expect, it rains most days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但只有在雨季时\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But it's only during the wet season
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,才会有如此倾盆大雨\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}that the rains become torrential.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,伴随着滂沱的大雨\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一种非凡无比的生物出现了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..comes a most remarkable creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,滑翔树蛙\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Gliding tree frogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,成千上万只树蛙涌来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Thousands drop in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,聚集在这片新形成的池塘中\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..to gather at this newly-formed pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,它们无不有着迫切的需要\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They all have an urgent need.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,繁殖\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}To breed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,雌性树蛙需要找一片树叶\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This female needs to find a leaf
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,从而在其上产卵\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and lay her eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这场繁殖的热潮只将持续一天\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The breeding frenzy will only last one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,因此它得抓紧时间了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..so she needs to get a move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,盼望得到垂青的雄性树蛙有很多\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}There are lots of eager males.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,九名候选者竞争一个席位\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Nine for every female.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,全都蓄势待发\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And all are ready to spring into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,因此对于雌性树蛙来说 寻求伴侣不成问题\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}So, for her, getting a partner is no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但失败者决定孤注一掷\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But the other males are desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对于雌性树蛙来说 求爱过程相当混乱\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}For this female, mating is rather chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,事情有些失控了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Things are getting out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有一种解决方法\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}There is one way to deal with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,踹它们几脚\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A few well-placed kicks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,往往卓有成效\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..usually does the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,问题解决了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Problem solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,现在雌性树蛙终于可以与伴侣结合\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}She and her partner can now finally mate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在一片相对平静的环境下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..in relative peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,树蛙产卵的位置\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The eggs are positioned perfectly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,恰好位于池塘正上方\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..directly overhanging the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是理想的蝌蚪育婴室\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This is the ideal nursery for tadpoles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如今 雌性树蛙的工作已经完成\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}For now, her work here is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,它将在明年大雨时分如期归来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}She'll be back next year when the heavy rains return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,淡水的出现\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}As quickly as freshwater appears...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有时稍纵即逝\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..it can vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,斯里兰卡东南部\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Southeast Sri Lanka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,正当旱季中期\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It's the middle of the dry season.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,方圆数里内 这是唯一一处水坑\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This is the only remaining water hole for miles around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,沼泽鳄\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Mugger crocodiles -
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,长达五米的巨型鳄鱼\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}giants, five metres long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,十数只沼泽鳄\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Dozens are hiding...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,潜藏于水面之下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..beneath the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还有更多鳄鱼\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And others...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,将来到此处\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..are on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这只雄性鳄鱼已经奔波了数小时\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This male has been travelling for hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这片水坑是它唯一有机会\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The water hole is the only place where he has a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,捕食鹿的地方\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}to catch a deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,只需捕食一只成年鹿 便足够沼泽鳄度过整个旱季\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A single adult would be enough to feed him for the entire dry season.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但猎物也已知晓敌人环伺在周围\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But hunting prey that knows you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,想要捕捉成功 就需要一些奇招\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..requires something truly remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沼泽鳄布置了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}He creates...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一个陷阱\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,它往泥里深挖\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}He digs down into the mud...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,直到身形被植被隐藏\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..deep enough to hide beneath the vegetation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,完美的伪装\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Perfect camouflage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沼泽鳄将陷阱布置在水边\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}He has built his trap right on the water's edge...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这里正是前来饮水的鹿的必经之处\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..so it's the first place that thirsty deer will come to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这些鳄鱼已经学会了如何利用\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}These crocodiles have learned to exploit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,鹿对于淡水的迫切需求\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}the deer's desperate need for freshwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:15:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,淡水不仅改变了动物的生命轨迹\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Freshwater transforms not only the lives of animals...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,还改变了整片地貌\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..but entire landscapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,每年 超过一万亿升水\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Every year, over a trillion litres of water
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,流入卡拉哈里沙漠\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}flow into the Kalahari Desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,水流自降雨地流到此处已经穿越了近两千公里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It has travelled a thousand miles from where it fell as rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,水流的到来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And on arrival...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,将卡拉哈里沙漠\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..it turns the Kalahari...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,变成了一片绿洲\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..into a vast oasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,奥卡万戈三角洲\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The Okavango Delta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,淡水吸引着数以百万计的动物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}These waters attract millions of animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对于一些动物来说 现在是组建家庭的绝佳时机\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And for some, now is the perfect time to raise a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,长脚水雉\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A lily-trotter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,它也是一名尽责的父亲\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And he is a father on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,雄性水雉养育着不止一只\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}He has not just one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,而是多达四只刚孵化的孩子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..but four newly-hatched chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,雏鸟六周后才能飞行\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They won't be able to fly for another six weeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,因此在那之前 只有成年雄性水雉才能保护它们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..so, until then, he alone is their protector.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,水上行走并非易事\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Walking on water is not straightforward...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,因此雄性水雉要教雏鸟如何在睡莲上行走\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..so he must show them how to be a lily-trotter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,高涨的水位使这里成为了绝佳的训练场\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The floodwaters make the perfect training ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,两周后\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And in two weeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,雏鸟不仅个头长大了一倍\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..his chicks not only double in size...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,信心也增加了一倍\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..they grow in confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但这里其实危机四伏\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But this is a dangerous place to stray.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,雄性水雉发出警报\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}He sounds the alarm,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,雏鸟便立刻停了下来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and his chicks instantly freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可它们还无法飞离险地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They can't yet fly to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但雄性水雉还有一种手段来保护雏鸟\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But there is one thing he can do to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:20:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一种风险极高的手段\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And it's risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近鳄鱼以分散它的注意力\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Get close enough to distract...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,试图将其引开\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..and hopefully divert the crocodile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大功告成\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:21:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,雄性水雉示意警报解除\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}He signals the all clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然而却少了一只雏鸟\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But one chick is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,雄性水雉的呼唤\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}His calls...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没有得到回应\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..go unanswered.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,有些蓬头垢面 但好在没丢掉性命\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A little bedraggled but alive and well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这只雏鸟只是没有听到父亲的呼唤而已\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}His chick just hadn't heard his call.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,危险来临时\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And when danger threatens,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.92,0:22:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,小心驶得万年船\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}its always better to be safe than sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,四只雏鸟在父亲的呵护下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}He's brought his chicks, all four of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.56,0:23:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,逐步迈向了独立的新生活\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}to the verge of independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.04,0:23:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然长脚水雉很好地适应了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Whilst lily-trotters are well adapted
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.76,0:23:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这片被洪水淹没的世界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}to life in this flooded world...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,三角洲的另一批居民却还没有适应\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..these residents of the delta are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.52,0:24:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,非洲野犬\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}African painted dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.28,0:24:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,通常情况下 它们是极成功的猎手\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Normally, they are remarkably successful hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.04,0:24:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但这五只野犬已经好几天没吃过东西了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But this pack of five hasn't eaten in days.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.04,0:24:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找猎物并不是问题\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Finding prey isn't the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.28,0:24:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,驴羚群就在数百米远处\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This herd of lechwe is only a few hundred metres away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.52,0:24:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但深不见底的水流挡住了去路\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But between them is deep water.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.80,0:25:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,从这里跨过去太危险了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It's not safe to cross here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.52,0:27:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,在陆地上 非洲野犬能以每小时60公里以上的速度奔驰\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}On dry land, the dogs can run at over 40mph.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.52,0:27:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但当驴羚遇到危险时 总是借助水域保护自己\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But when threatened, lechwe always seek the safety of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.28,0:27:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,它们有着分叉的蹄子和长长的后腿\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}With their splayed hooves and long hind legs,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.64,0:27:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,能够在水中大步向前\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}they can power their way through the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.04,0:27:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,非洲野犬却不行\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The dogs can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.04,0:28:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,非洲野犬虽然水性略逊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The pack won't be able to outswim the lechwe.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.36,0:28:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但它们有一种策略\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But they do have a strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.76,0:28:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,非洲野犬将驴羚赶向自己的主场\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The dogs drive the lechwe to where they have the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.76,0:28:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,赶回陆地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Back towards dry land.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.28,0:29:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 野犬夺回了优势\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Now the pack can regain lost ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.64,0:29:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是成功了 但明天能否继续成功还是未知数\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Success today, but tomorrow the pack will need to hunt again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.76,0:30:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,在奥卡万戈三角洲\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}In the Okavango,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.48,0:30:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,动物必须适应这里时有时无的淡水\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}animals must always adapt to the coming and going of freshwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.76,0:30:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但在一些罕见之处 比如马拉维湖\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But there are a few rare places, as here in Lake Malawi,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.76,0:30:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,淡水数百万年不间断的存在\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}where freshwater has lain for millions of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.36,0:30:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这使生命得以进化\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And that has enabled life to evolve
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.52,0:30:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,形成了此处千姿百态的丰富物种\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}into a dazzling diversity of species.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.44,0:30:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这里孕育着数以千计不同的鱼类\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}There are over a thousand different kinds of fish here...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.28,0:30:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,比地球上任何一处湖泊都多\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..more than any other lake on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.04,0:31:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,水中各色物种的竞争激烈异常\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Competition in these waters is intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.92,0:31:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是利氏雨丽鱼 也称迷彩鲷\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Meet Nimbochromis livingstonii.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.52,0:31:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一名骗术高手\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A master of deception
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.80,0:31:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,假装自己已经死了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}that tricks other fish into thinking it's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.04,0:31:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,迷彩鲷身上斑驳的色彩看上去如同腐烂的肉体\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Its mottled colouration mimics decaying flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.52,0:31:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但想要装死\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But to appear dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.04,0:31:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,迷彩鲷必须\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..one must at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.92,0:32:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如尸体般一动不动\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..act dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.52,0:32:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这条年轻的迷彩鲷骗不到任何鱼\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This juvenile is fooling no-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.84,0:32:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也许假装猝死会更可信\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Perhaps faking his death will be more believable.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.04,0:32:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,搞砸了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Blown it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.04,0:32:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,演技还需进一步打磨\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A more subtle performance will be needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.28,0:33:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这次更逼真了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This is more convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.40,0:33:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但显然还需要继续提高\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But his aim must be better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.68,0:33:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就差一点\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Nearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.76,0:33:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,看来得换一个地方了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It seems he's overstayed his welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.68,0:34:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一次尝试\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}In a final effort...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.88,0:34:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,迷彩鲷似乎甚至屏住了呼吸\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..he appears to even hold his breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.04,0:34:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,终于成功了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Success at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.28,0:35:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切需要生物百万年来的演化\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}All it took was a million years of evolution...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.28,0:35:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,以及这片湖泊历久弥坚的稳定性\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..and the unique stability of this ancient lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.76,0:35:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,赤道非洲的西海岸外\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Off the western coast of Equatorial Africa
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.68,0:35:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,坐落着比奥科火山岛\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}lies the volcanic island of Bioko.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.04,0:36:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的淡水十分汹涌\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Freshwater here has a turbulent nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.04,0:36:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很少有生命敢于冒险入水\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Few venture into such waters,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.52,0:36:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但风险越高 收益越高\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}but for those that do, there can be great rewards.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.04,0:36:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,经过几个月的海中觅食与生长\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}After months feeding and growing out at sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.20,0:36:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这些虾虎鱼已经做好了繁殖的准备\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}these gobies are ready to breed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.52,0:36:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,最安全的产卵处\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And the safest place to lay their eggs
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.68,0:37:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是海洋捕食者无法染指的地方\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}is somewhere that ocean predators can't reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.04,0:37:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这座瀑布顶端\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The top of this waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.28,0:37:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对鱼来说 无疑是一处不可能的目的地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Surely an impossible journey for a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.76,0:37:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但在接下来的几天里 虾虎鱼会改变自己\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But over the coming days, the gobies transform themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.28,0:37:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,颜色发生变化\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They change colour.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.04,0:37:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴部转动 如同一个吸盘\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Their mouth rotates and acts like a kind of suction cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.52,0:37:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是它们需要的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..which they will certainly need.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.52,0:37:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,华山一条路 它们必须登上顶端\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Because the only way...is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.76,0:38:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,垂直落差高达30米\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It is 30 metres to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.52,0:38:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而虾虎鱼身长只有不到3厘米\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They are only an inch long.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.04,0:38:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,相当于人类去攀登\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This is the equivalent of a human being scaling a waterfall
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.52,0:38:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,近两公里高的瀑布\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}over a mile high.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.04,0:38:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,数以百万计的虾虎鱼向顶端进发\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Millions attempt the climb...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.04,0:38:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但只有不到1%能成功登顶\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..but less than 1% will make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.28,0:39:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这只虾虎鱼已经爬了好几天了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This goby has been climbing for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.28,0:39:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.36,0:39:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,抵达瀑布顶端的虾虎鱼现在可以准备繁殖了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Those that reach the top can now prepare to breed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.04,0:39:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,时机成熟时 虾虎鱼幼崽将被湍流冲回大海\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And when the time comes, their young will be washed back out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.28,0:40:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,流水的非凡力量\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The extraordinary power of flowing water
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.04,0:40:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,使其成为地球上最伟大的建筑师\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}makes it our planet's greatest architect.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.04,0:40:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的地表看上去仿佛如同外星世界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This may look like the surface of an alien planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.52,0:40:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但这些奇异的图案实际上是通往海洋的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..but these strange patterns are channels of freshwater...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.36,0:40:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一条条淡水河道\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..flowing towards the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.04,0:41:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,38亿年来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}For 3.8 billion years,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.04,0:41:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,自从第一滴雨水洒落大地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}ever since the first rains fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.28,0:41:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,淡水便无休止的循环往复\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..freshwater has been making this journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.28,0:41:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,然而今天 世界上三分之二的大江大河\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But today, two thirds of our world's great rivers
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.04,0:41:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,已不再入海\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}no longer reach the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.04,0:42:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上淡水资源有限\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}There is a finite amount of freshwater on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.52,0:42:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因此人类设计了非凡的方法\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..so humans have devised extraordinary means
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.36,0:42:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,来确保有足够淡水满足我们的需求\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}to ensure that it is always available to meet our every demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.32,0:42:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们如今大规模地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}We now control freshwater...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.04,0:42:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,控制淡水资源\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..on a colossal scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.04,0:43:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上最大的灌溉系统\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The largest irrigation system on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.04,0:43:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,建于巴基斯坦\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}has been built here in Pakistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.52,0:43:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个由水坝和运河组成的巨大网络\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A vast network of dams and canals...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.04,0:43:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,从而从印度河中引水配水\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..that diverts and drains the great Indus River.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.52,0:43:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,整个系统被用来灌溉一片英国大小的区域\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It's used to irrigate an area the size of England.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.04,0:43:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这片人造淡水世界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This man-made freshwater world
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.88,0:43:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,为数百万人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}provides water and a livelihood
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.76,0:43:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,提供了水资源和生计\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}for millions of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.96,0:44:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是以自然世界的损害为代价的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..but at a cost to the natural world.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.52,0:44:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一种稀有的生物被困于灌溉渠中\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A rare creature has become stranded in this irrigation canal.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.52,0:44:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,渠中的水很快就将消失\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And the water will soon be gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.48,0:44:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,以供应周围土地的需要\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}used to supply the surrounding land.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.28,0:44:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这种生物濒临灭绝 数量不足2000只\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Endangered, they number fewer than 2,000 individuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.76,0:44:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,印度河豚\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}An Indus river dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.28,0:45:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这只雌性印度河豚的位置距离干流240公里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This female dolphin is 150 miles from the main river.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.76,0:45:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,它无法靠自己的力量回去\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}She can't return on her own,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.40,0:45:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,因此唯一的选择就是由救援队救走它\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}so the only option is for this rescue team to take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.52,0:45:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,离开水 印度河豚无法生存太久\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Out of water, she cannot survive for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.04,0:46:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,回到河流的路途将花费数小时\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The journey back to the river will take hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.04,0:46:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,它的生命如今只能指望救援队\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Her life now depends on these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.76,0:48:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,仅一个月便有近30只印度河豚陷入危险 不得不依靠救援\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Nearly 30 dolphins had to be rescued in one month alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.76,0:48:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,淡水不仅是人类的资源\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Freshwater is not only a resource for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.28,0:48:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,更是无数物种的家园\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It is the home for countless species
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.04,0:49:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没有淡水 便无法生存\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}that simply cannot survive without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.04,0:49:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,淡水是地球的命脉\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Freshwater is the lifeblood of Planet Earth.
