Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.02,0:49:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(184,250)}{\fs22\fnMicrosoft YaHei\c&HD5D5D5&\2a&FF\bord0\blur0\shad0\fad(255,0,255,400,800,4960,5240)}{\blur7}{\t(400,800,\blur0)}{\kt40\K40 }后
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.02,0:49:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(200,250)}{\fs22\fnMicrosoft YaHei\c&HD5D5D5&\2a&FF\bord0\blur0\shad0\fad(255,0,255,800,1200,4960,5240)}{\blur7}{\t(800,1200,\blur0)}{\kt80\K40 }花
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.02,0:49:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(216,250)}{\fs22\fnMicrosoft YaHei\c&HD5D5D5&\2a&FF\bord0\blur0\shad0\fad(255,0,255,1200,1600,4960,5240)}{\blur7}{\t(1200,16 00,\blur0)}{\kt120\K40 }絮
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.04,0:49:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,为了拍摄最濒危的淡水河豚\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}To film the story of the most endangered freshwater dolphin,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.52,0:49:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,「地球脉动」摄制组与世界顶尖专家乌兹玛·汗展开合作\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}the Planet Earth team joined the world's leading expert - Uzma Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.28,0:50:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次见到印度河豚时 简直惊呆了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The first time I saw Indus dolphin, I was just amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.52,0:50:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,它是一种美丽的生物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It's a beautiful creature, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.52,0:50:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我对它一见钟情 它太独特了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}it's like love at first sight. It's so unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.76,0:50:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,20年来 乌兹玛一直在研究印度河豚的种群数量\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Uzma has been studying the last remaining population for over 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.28,0:50:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有一只印度河豚冒出水面\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}There's a dolphin that surfaced just right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.96,0:50:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,印度河豚只能存活于淡水中\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Indus river dolphin can only live in freshwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.56,0:50:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,只分布于巴基斯坦\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It is only found in Pakistan and nowhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.76,0:50:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,印度河中只剩下约2000只了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And we only have about 2,000 of them left in the Indus River.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.04,0:50:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,每一只印度河豚都弥足珍贵\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}So, you know, each individual is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.32,0:50:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在浑浊的水中跟随印度河豚十分困难\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Following the dolphins in the murky water is extremely challenging.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.32,0:50:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,它们跃出水面的瞬间稍纵即逝\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They only surface for a split second
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.32,0:50:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这也使得保护它们变得困难\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and that makes protecting them difficult, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.04,0:50:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对它们最大的威胁是会被困在灌溉渠里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Their greatest threat is becoming trapped in the irrigation canals.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.04,0:51:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但乌兹玛也许有一种解决方案\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But Uzma may have a solution,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.80,0:51:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她与救援队展开合作\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and teams up with a rescue unit...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.04,0:51:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,以尝试一些新东西\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..to attempt something never done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.08,0:51:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们第一次在亚洲的河豚上\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This is the first time we'll be putting satellite tags
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.04,0:51:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,设置卫星标记\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}on river dolphins in Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.04,0:51:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,传感器还没有进行过这类物种的测试\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Sensors has not been tested on this species,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.04,0:51:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有点担心 但如果运行顺利\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}there's a little bit of anxiety, but if they work,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.36,0:51:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这将是物种保护工作的一个突破\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}then it's going to be a breakthrough for conservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.40,0:51:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,十数年来 乌兹玛一直在开发一种合适的标记\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Uzma has been developing a suitable tag for over ten years
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.40,0:51:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,希望这能帮助她收集\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and hopes it will help her collect critical data
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.52,0:51:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,河豚如何跨越水坝和运河的关键数据\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}on how the dolphins are moving through the dams and canals.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.28,0:51:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但为了能够标记河豚 必须先有河豚得到救援\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But in order to tag, she will first need a successful rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.70,0:51:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们今天的救援计划\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This is the plan for ou rescue today.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.04,0:52:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,每次救援时 我都很担心\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}I'm usually very concerned when a rescue is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.88,0:52:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,别让水进到呼吸孔里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Don't let water get in the blowhole
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.52,0:52:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,也别挤压河豚\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and don't squeeze too tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.52,0:52:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,潜水员实际上经验丰富\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}You know, the divers, they are very experienced,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.04,0:52:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但我总是会有些担心\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}but a part of me is always very worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.28,0:52:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,它们是人类从未应对过的野生动物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They are wild animals that have never been handled.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.44,0:52:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,救援队这项工作真的很冒险\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It's really quite a risky thing that they're undertaking here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.52,0:52:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,河豚很有可能活不下来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}There's a good chance the dolphin might die.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.76,0:52:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果不尝试救援\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But, of course, they're balancing that against the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.52,0:52:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,它们一定会死\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}that they definitely will die if they stay in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.04,0:52:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所以必须冒这个险\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}so it's a risk they have to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.28,0:52:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们救起河豚了吗 -是的 救起来了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Have they got the dolphin? Yeah, I think so. They've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.52,0:53:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是生死时速\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Now speed is key.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.52,0:53:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在正全速赶往放生地点\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}We're now bombing across the field on the way to the release site,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.00,0:53:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为乌兹玛在我们前头\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and I think Uzma went ahead of us, so I'm really hopeful
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.52,0:53:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,希望她能有机会设下标记\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}that she'll get her opportunity to tag the dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.76,0:53:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但救援任务有时也会偏离轨迹\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But rescue missions don't always go to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.12,0:53:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.36,0:53:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,轮胎被扎破了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A puncture.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.96,0:53:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 抬起床垫\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Hey, come here! Grab the mattress!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.52,0:53:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,河豚被快速转移到摄制组的车上\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The dolphin is quickly moved to the film crew's truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.52,0:53:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,把水箱拿过来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Bring the water tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.76,0:53:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,把它放在更里面点\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Put it further forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.40,0:54:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但由于没有遮蔽物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But with no roof for shelter,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.04,0:54:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,河豚脱水而死的风险更高了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}the dolphin is at greater risk of dehydration.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.76,0:54:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕是现在 风险也很高\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The stakes are high, even right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.36,0:54:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一只可爱的小动物 我们不希望它失去生命\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It's a cute little animal and we don't want it to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.68,0:54:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,慢点慢点\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Slow, slow, slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.44,0:54:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,团队改道前往距离最近的放生地点\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The team re-route to the closest release site.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.28,0:54:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再拖了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}There can be no more delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.52,0:54:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,乌兹玛取消了标记计划\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Uzma calls off the tagging.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.52,0:55:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这很不幸 因为我们已经做好了准备\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It's unfortunate because we were all prepared,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.20,0:55:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一大早我们就准备就绪 非常兴奋\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}we were very excited since morning, all geared up,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.28,0:55:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,希望下次救援行动能有机会设置标记\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}but hopefully we'll get an opportunity to tag the next rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.76,0:55:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,几天后 乌兹玛终于等到了机会\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A few days later, Uzma finally gets her chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.32,0:55:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,很激动的一天\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It's a very exciting day for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.36,0:55:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.28,0:55:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这一刻我们等待了十多年\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The moment that we have been waiting for, over ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.24,0:55:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静下来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Just stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.24,0:55:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 可以了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}OK, it's good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.12,0:55:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.36,0:55:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,干得好\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.76,0:56:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴 特别高兴\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}I am very happy, very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.32,0:56:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这是个了不起的成就\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}I think it's a great accomplishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.04,0:56:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我人生中最高兴的一刻\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It's the happiest moment of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.52,0:56:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,几周中 标记开始帮助我们能更多的了解印度河豚\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Within a few weeks, the tags begin to reveal some new insights.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.28,0:56:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,它们移动的很频繁 这是我们从未预料到的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They are moving quite a lot, which we never expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.12,0:56:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一只河豚从放生处逆流而上46公里之远\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}So one of the dolphins actually went about 46km upstream
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.28,0:56:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个新发现就是\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}from the release site, and the other thing is that we thought
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.84,0:56:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们本以为河豚会留在河流干流\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}that they will stay in the main river stream,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.28,0:56:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但实际上它们经常会游进支流中 特别有意思\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}but they are using side channels. It is extremely interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.28,0:56:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,追踪受标记河豚的动向\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Tracking the movement of the tagged dolphins
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.24,0:56:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,将帮助乌兹玛更好的了解\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}will help Uzma better understand
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.52,0:56:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,它们被困的时间与地点\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}when and where they become trapped...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.76,0:57:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这将帮助保护这种濒危动物未来的生存\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..helping safeguard the future of this most endangered animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.76,0:57:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,下一集\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Next time...
