Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.84,0:57:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一片隐蔽的世界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A hidden world...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.00,0:57:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 生命以出人意料的方式\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..where lives are intimately entwined...
